                            <p class="msg-principal">Om Namo Venkatesaya! A warm welcome to one and all. As Principal of the renowned College, I am honoured to present to you a brief profile of 
                            Sri Padmavathi Women’s Degree and P.G.College, (A) Tirupati with its Septuagenarian existence. The College was meant to provide education and 
                            empowerment to all the women of Rayalaseema region. The student saplings of yester years have grown tall and big with a strong sense of confidence 
                            and scattered all over the globe,spreading the name of the College far and wide, bringing in more numberof educators to choose the Institution 
                            as safe haven to their girl children to stay and study. Thanks to the TTD management for its great work of giving it a good building for the 
                            colleges and hostels, their by standing for bringing up generations of young women and carving them with holistic personalities to serve the 
                            cause of society as well as the nation. Academics, Co-Curriculars and extra-Curricular activities flourish with a strong backdrop of committed 
                            faculty in all aspects. Given the incredible infrastructure and ISO certified status in various aspects,the college is for sure, a venue for 
                            proving its worth and standing to fulfill the requirements of NAAC and be placed at A+ in the recent Accreditation exercise. The years old 
                            dream of achieving Autonomous Status also was realised with the extraordinary support and commitment extended by the TTDs. Years of  services 
                            rendered by the dedicated Principals and their teaching and non - teaching staff have given the college an unchallenging reputation. We stand as one. 
                            Of course the spirit of team work is key behind our excellence and success. We strive for it. We stand for it. We Welcome you to join this team and 
                            be part of it. Thank You. “Vina Venkatesam na naatho na naatha, sada Venkatesam smarami smarami”.</p>
                        </div>
                        <!-- <div class="modal-footer">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Save changes</button>
                        </div> -->
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <style>
            .about-area p {
    font-family: 'Lexend', sans-serif;
            }
                button.close.popup {
                    position: absolute;
                    opacity: 1;
                    right: -10px;
                    background: #F44336;
                    color: #fff;
                    width: 25px;
                    height: 25px;
                    font-size: 25px;
                    line-height: 15px;
                    border-radius: 50%;
                    top: -10px;
                    font-weight: 500;
                    transition: 0.5s all;
                }

                button.close.popup:hover {
                    background: #fff;
                    color: #F44336;
                    transition: 0.5s all;
                }

                .modal-body.popup {
                    padding: 0;
                }

                div#naacPopup {
                    z-index: 99;
                }

                .modal-backdrop.show {
                    opacity: 0;
                    z-index: 98;
                }

                @media screen and (max-width: 575px) {

                    a.elem img {
                        height: 215px !important;
                        object-position: top;
                    }
                }
            </style>
            <script>
                function snow() {
                    var duration = 25 * 1000;
                    var animationEnd = Date.now() + duration;
                    var skew = 1;

                    function randomInRange(min, max) {
                        return Math.random() * (max - min) + min;
                    }

                    (function frame() {
                        var timeLeft = animationEnd - Date.now();
                        var ticks = Math.max(200, 500 * (timeLeft / duration));
                        skew = Math.max(0.8, skew - 0.001);

                        confetti({
                            particleCount: 2,
                            startVelocity: 0,
                            ticks: ticks,
                            origin: {
                                x: Math.random(),
                                // since particles fall down, skew start toward the top
                                y: (Math.random() * skew) - 0.2
                            },
                            colors: ['#FF5722'],
                            shapes: ['circle'],
                            gravity: randomInRange(0.4, 0.6),
                            scalar: randomInRange(0.4, 1),
                            drift: randomInRange(-0.4, 0.4)
                        });

                        //   if (timeLeft > 0) {
                        //     requestAnimationFrame(frame);
                        //   }
                        if (Date.now() < Date.now() + 15000) {
                            id = requestAnimationFrame(frame);
                        }
                    }());
                }

                $(window).on('load', function() {
                    // $('#naacPopup').modal('show');
                    // $('#naacPopup').modal({
                    //     backdrop: 'static',
                    //     keyboard: false
                    // }, 'show');
                    // snow();
                });
                
                $(document).ready(function() {
            // Check if the script has already been executed in this session
            if (!sessionStorage.getItem('scriptExecuted')) {
                // Your jQuery script goes here
                $('#naacPopup').modal({
                        backdrop: 'static',
                        keyboard: false
                    }, 'show');
                    snow();
                // console.log("Script is executing for the first time in this session.");
                
                // Mark script as executed in sessionStorage
                sessionStorage.setItem('scriptExecuted', 'true');
            } else {
                console.log("Script already executed in this session.");
            }
        });

                function stopanimation() {
                    window.cancelAnimationFrame(id);
                }
            </script>
            <style>
